EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO MOTOR AND OTHER VEHICLES -- REGISTRATION OF VEHICLES
***
1 This act would allow for a special Rhode Island license plate to raise awareness for colon
2 cancer. The plate would be designed by the Partnership to Reduce Cancer in Rhode Island. The
3 fees for the plate would be divided equally between the general fund and the not-for-profit
4 Partnership to Reduce Cancer in Rhode Island.
5 This act would take effect upon passage.
